  intro: 'Bridgeport homeowners trust our verified contractors for full roof replacement. Classic Chicago bungalows on streets like Halsted, Lowe, and Morgan, two-flats, and brick homes throughout this neighborhood all have distinct roofing needs our contractors know well.',
