  intro: 'All 6 contractors serve the Near West Side. Home to the United Center, Greektown, and University Village, this neighborhood has diverse housing stock from vintage two-flats on Taylor Street to newer townhomes near the medical district.',
  introEs: 'Los 6 contratistas sirven el Near West Side. Hogar del United Center, Greektown y University Village, con viviendas diversas desde two-flats vintage en Taylor Street hasta townhomes más nuevos cerca del distrito médico.',
